{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend the RTI deadline of 19 March for contractors and employees for the CJRS",
        "additional_details": "By imposing this requirement, thousands of employees are being unfairly excluded from the furlough scheme and is putting us all in a seriously risky position. This requirement of the 19th of March needs to be moved to include employees who received their first pay in April for work completed in March.",
        "background": "Contractors who recently changed over to an umbrella company in March or employees who started a new position or new contract in March, should be included in the furlough scheme regardless of the fact that an RTI submission wasn\u2019t submitted before 19th of March.",
